title: Prince William brings children to see their newborn brother
text:
Prince William brings children to see their newborn brother 5:23pm BST - 00:51 
Prince William brought George and Charlotte to St Mary's hospital to see their mother, the Duchess of Cambridge, and to meet their new brother. Rough cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
